objects.string:
Distinctive Features :
Longer rather than wider, Eggshell White coloring, cluster of roughly 4-6 eggs, stable arranging pattern

objects.name: Raptor_Info
objects.string:
Utahraptor ostrommaysorum :
One of the geologically oldest and largest known dromaeosaurids. Large sickle claw roughly 9.5 inches long. Being roughly 20 feet long and around 5 feet tall at the hip.
